<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَنْ أَبِي الدَّيْلَمِ زَاذُويَهْ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَمِعَ ابنَ عَبَّاسٍ، قَوْلَهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سَمِعَ مِنْهُ عُمَرُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> بنُ يُونُسَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (ث): "زاذو"، وفي (س): "زادوني".<br>(٢) في (ث): "سمع عمر".</p> </div>